00:00:06.774 --> 00:00:08.041 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>And we're back with</i>

00:00:08.075 --> 00:00:09.711 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>the national tournament</i>
 <i>finals.</i>

00:00:09.744 --> 00:00:12.514 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>After the first 60 minutes</i>
 <i>ended with a tied match,</i>

00:00:12.547 --> 00:00:15.415 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>the executives decided</i>
 <i>to have extra time.</i>

00:00:15.449 --> 00:00:18.653 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>This means two half times</i>
 <i>of 10 minutes each.</i>

00:00:18.686 --> 00:00:19.854 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>If a tie happens,</i>

00:00:19.888 --> 00:00:21.288 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>both teams</i>
 <i>will be crowned</i>

00:00:21.321 --> 00:00:23.223 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>tournament champions.</i>

00:00:23.257 --> 00:00:24.491 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>Despite his injuries,</i>

00:00:24.526 --> 00:00:26.828 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu's captain,</i>
 <i>Tsubasa Ozora,</i>

00:00:26.861 --> 00:00:28.161 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>will stay on the pitch.</i>

00:00:28.195 --> 00:00:29.964 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>And the white team</i>
 <i>is going to start</i>

00:00:29.998 --> 00:00:31.164 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>with the kick-off.</i>

00:00:31.198 --> 00:00:32.399 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>I relied way too much</i>

00:00:32.432 --> 00:00:34.736 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>on my Drive Shot</i>
 <i>to win this.</i>

00:00:34.769 --> 00:00:38.405 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I didn't think I could</i>
 <i>score on Toho otherwise.</i>

00:00:38.438 --> 00:00:42.777 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>In a way, I'm still</i>
 <i>depending on Roberto.</i>

00:00:42.810 --> 00:00:44.411 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>And not just on him,</i>

00:00:44.444 --> 00:00:48.181 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>but Misaki, Wakabayashi,</i>
 <i>Ishizaki...</i>

00:00:48.215 --> 00:00:49.483 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>On the whole team...</i>

00:00:49.517 --> 00:00:50.484 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Go, Team!
-[Tsubasa] <i>On Sanae...</i>

00:00:50.518 --> 00:00:51.251 position:24% line:89% align:start
You guys can do it!

00:00:51.285 --> 00:00:52.620 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Hooray! Hooray!
-Hooray! Hooray!

00:00:52.654 --> 00:00:53.788 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Let's win now.
-[Tsubasa] <i>Everyone's backed</i>

00:00:53.821 --> 00:00:55.623 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>me up until now...</i>

00:00:55.657 --> 00:00:56.558 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>but after this...</i>

00:00:57.357 --> 00:00:59.727 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll have to</i>
 <i>fend for myself.</i>

00:00:59.761 --> 00:01:01.629 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>When I play in Brazil.</i>

00:01:01.663 --> 00:01:02.530 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Alone.</i>

00:01:02.564 --> 00:01:04.064 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Dear friends,</i>
 <i>I appreciate you</i>

00:01:04.097 --> 00:01:05.265 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>from the bottom of my heart</i>

00:01:05.299 --> 00:01:06.801 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>for going with me</i>
 <i>on this journey.</i>

00:01:06.834 --> 00:01:07.902 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:01:07.936 --> 00:01:09.637 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>I am Tsubasa Ozora,</i>

00:01:09.671 --> 00:01:13.473 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>and my last goal in Japan</i>
 <i>is my farewell present!</i>

00:02:53.775 --> 00:02:54.909 position:24% line:77% align:start
-[narr] <i>Episode 51:</i>
-[ann] <i>Welcome back!</i>

00:02:54.942 --> 00:02:56.209 position:41% line:77% align:start
[narr]
 <i>Miracle Drive Shot!</i>

00:02:56.243 --> 00:02:58.311 position:10% line:77% align:start
[ann] <i>This is the first half</i>
 <i>of the extra time</i>

00:02:58.345 --> 00:02:59.479 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>and Tsubasa has the ball.</i>

00:02:59.514 --> 00:03:01.949 position:24% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa can't move
as fast anymore, Koike.

00:03:01.983 --> 00:03:03.316 position:27% line:83% align:start
It'll be a breeze
to take the ball.

00:03:03.350 --> 00:03:04.351 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-Huh?

00:03:05.053 --> 00:03:06.154 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Impossible!
-Impossible!

00:03:06.186 --> 00:03:07.522 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>He fooled them so easily.</i>

00:03:07.555 --> 00:03:11.291 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Incredible. He still has</i>
 <i>the energy to play.</i>

00:03:11.324 --> 00:03:13.061 position:27% line:83% align:start
-We'll teach you!
-We'll show you!

00:03:13.094 --> 00:03:14.194 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[ann] <i>Tsubasa evades</i>

00:03:14.227 --> 00:03:15.262 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>those sliding tackles</i>

00:03:15.295 --> 00:03:16.097 position:30% line:83% align:start
- <i>with a jump.</i>
-[gasps]

00:03:16.130 --> 00:03:17.264 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:03:17.297 --> 00:03:19.534 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa, what are you</i>
 <i>made out of?</i>

00:03:19.567 --> 00:03:21.234 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>How can you keep running</i>
 <i>like that</i>

00:03:21.268 --> 00:03:23.037 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>with your injuries,</i>
 <i>young man?</i>

00:03:23.071 --> 00:03:24.138 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Takeshi] Tsubasa!
-Huh?

00:03:24.172 --> 00:03:26.206 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm going to steal the ball.

00:03:27.340 --> 00:03:28.275 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[eagle screech]
-[Takeshi] [yell]

00:03:28.308 --> 00:03:29.510 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Sawada slides,</i>

00:03:29.544 --> 00:03:32.212 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>but Tsubasa protects</i>
 <i>the ball with both feet.</i>

00:03:32.245 --> 00:03:33.413 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:03:33.447 --> 00:03:35.215 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>This ball belongs to me.</i>

00:03:35.248 --> 00:03:37.151 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's mine and no one else's.</i>

00:03:37.185 --> 00:03:39.187 position:19% line:83% align:start
Quickly, don't let him
get any closer.

00:03:39.219 --> 00:03:40.387 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:03:42.056 --> 00:03:43.591 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Not again.</i>

00:03:43.624 --> 00:03:44.759 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>I feel as if...</i>

00:03:45.593 --> 00:03:47.628 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>as if my body</i>
 <i>was weakening...</i>

00:03:48.996 --> 00:03:50.131 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>No...</i>

00:03:50.164 --> 00:03:51.331 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>I can't give up now.</i>

00:03:52.365 --> 00:03:54.702 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I have to score.</i>
 <i>Everyone's counting on me.</i>

00:03:54.736 --> 00:03:55.737 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:03:56.537 --> 00:03:57.605 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[gasp]
-[ann] <i>And Tsubasa</i>

00:03:57.638 --> 00:03:59.439 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>keeps fooling</i>
 <i>Toho's defense.</i>

00:03:59.473 --> 00:04:00.742 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
-Tsubasa!

00:04:00.775 --> 00:04:01.843 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
-[gasp]

00:04:01.876 --> 00:04:02.944 position:30% line:89% align:start
You can do it!

00:04:02.977 --> 00:04:03.811 position:41% line:89% align:start
[pant]

00:04:03.845 --> 00:04:04.411 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa...</i>

00:04:05.312 --> 00:04:07.682 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>before you joined</i>
 <i>Team Nankatsu...</i>

00:04:07.715 --> 00:04:10.818 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>the ball was</i>
 <i>the only friend you had.</i>

00:04:10.852 --> 00:04:12.053 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>You surprised Wakabayashi</i>

00:04:12.086 --> 00:04:15.656 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and outran all of team</i>
 <i>Shutetsu without any help.</i>

00:04:15.690 --> 00:04:18.726 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>But you're not alone</i>
 <i>anymore, my friend.</i>

00:04:18.760 --> 00:04:20.460 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:04:21.461 --> 00:04:23.330 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's as far as you get.

00:04:24.098 --> 00:04:25.298 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-[ann] <i>In spite of</i>

00:04:25.332 --> 00:04:27.135 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>his injuries,</i>
 <i>Tsubasa demonstrates</i>

00:04:27.168 --> 00:04:28.770 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>his prowess on the pitch.</i>

00:04:28.803 --> 00:04:29.871 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>An absolute genius,</i>

00:04:29.904 --> 00:04:33.306 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>a prodigy of soccer</i>
 <i>like no one's seen before.</i>

00:04:33.340 --> 00:04:34.509 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Without a doubt,</i>

00:04:34.542 --> 00:04:38.278 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa Ozora is</i>
 <i>Japanese soccer's promise.</i>

00:04:38.311 --> 00:04:41.215 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Toho's defense</i>
 <i>simply can't stop him.</i>

00:04:41.249 --> 00:04:43.450 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[cheering]
-Come on, guys!

00:04:43.483 --> 00:04:46.254 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>I have...</i>
 <i>I have to shoot.</i>

00:04:46.286 --> 00:04:48.256 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm going to score</i>
 <i>with this shot.</i>

00:04:48.288 --> 00:04:49.957 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:04:49.991 --> 00:04:51.058 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>But Hyuga the Tiger</i>

00:04:51.092 --> 00:04:53.326 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>runs to face him head on,</i>
 <i>and defend his goal.</i>

00:04:53.360 --> 00:04:55.096 position:21% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa, what're you
waiting for?

00:04:55.129 --> 00:04:56.063 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Fight me head on.
-[grunt]

00:04:57.165 --> 00:04:58.566 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa winds up</i>
 <i>to shoot.</i>

00:04:58.599 --> 00:04:59.734 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>Will Hyuga be able to</i>

00:04:59.767 --> 00:05:02.036 position:16% line:83% align:start
- <i>stop the shot on time?</i>
-[tiger growl]

00:05:02.069 --> 00:05:03.204 position:24% line:89% align:start
Get a load of this!

00:05:03.237 --> 00:05:05.573 position:24% line:89% align:start
Sliding Tiger Shot!

00:05:05.606 --> 00:05:08.109 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Hyuga reacts</i>
 <i>a tenth of a second faster</i>

00:05:08.142 --> 00:05:08.876 position:27% line:83% align:start
- <i>and the ball is</i>
-[yelling]

00:05:08.910 --> 00:05:10.278 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>sent out flying.</i>

00:05:10.310 --> 00:05:12.379 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-Impossible!

00:05:13.147 --> 00:05:14.314 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Ryo]
Tsubasa...

00:05:14.347 --> 00:05:15.382 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:05:16.383 --> 00:05:17.752 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[groaning]
-Ishizaki...

00:05:17.785 --> 00:05:20.320 position:41% line:83% align:start
[groan]
Don't you forget it.

00:05:20.353 --> 00:05:21.388 position:33% line:89% align:start
All of us...

00:05:22.322 --> 00:05:24.525 position:10% line:89% align:start
Everyone is your friend now!

00:05:24.559 --> 00:05:26.260 position:16% line:83% align:start
-And we're by your side!
-And we're by your side!

00:05:26.294 --> 00:05:27.028 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:05:27.061 --> 00:05:28.296 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's right, Captain.

00:05:28.328 --> 00:05:29.329 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're not alone.

00:05:29.362 --> 00:05:31.199 position:16% line:89% align:start
We'll always back you up.

00:05:31.232 --> 00:05:34.035 position:19% line:89% align:start
Right now, and always!

00:05:34.068 --> 00:05:35.303 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Ishizaki...</i>

00:05:35.335 --> 00:05:36.704 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>My friends...</i>

00:05:36.737 --> 00:05:37.805 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Thank you...</i>

00:05:37.839 --> 00:05:38.906 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Honestly...</i>

00:05:40.241 --> 00:05:41.275 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:05:41.309 --> 00:05:43.211 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>I won't dare waste...</i>

00:05:43.244 --> 00:05:44.812 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>your gift.</i>

00:05:44.846 --> 00:05:45.880 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:05:45.913 --> 00:05:46.446 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa!</i>

00:05:47.480 --> 00:05:49.984 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>My friends have always</i>
 <i>been there for me</i>

00:05:50.017 --> 00:05:51.786 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>no matter what happens.</i>

00:05:51.819 --> 00:05:53.054 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Now I know...</i>

00:05:53.087 --> 00:05:54.589 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>that even if I'm far,</i>

00:05:54.622 --> 00:05:56.190 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>they will be with me.</i>

00:05:56.224 --> 00:05:58.458 position:30% line:83% align:start
Do it, Tsubasa!
Score a goal!

00:05:59.359 --> 00:06:00.561 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>All of my friends</i>
 <i>have helped me</i>

00:06:00.595 --> 00:06:02.462 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>every step of the way.</i>

00:06:04.932 --> 00:06:07.168 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Look at this!</i>
 <i>Tsubasa's winding up</i>

00:06:07.201 --> 00:06:09.036 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>for what looks to be</i>
 <i>the last shot.</i>

00:06:09.070 --> 00:06:10.238 position:10% line:89% align:start
What's the hold up, Tsubasa?

00:06:10.271 --> 00:06:12.340 position:16% line:83% align:start
That's not what Tsubasa's
Drive Shot

00:06:12.372 --> 00:06:13.440 position:21% line:89% align:start
normally looks like.

00:06:13.473 --> 00:06:16.344 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>This will be</i>
 <i>my last shot in Japan.</i>

00:06:16.376 --> 00:06:18.179 position:30% line:89% align:start
[eagle screech]

00:06:18.212 --> 00:06:21.148 position:27% line:83% align:start
I will make this
a parting gift...

00:06:21.182 --> 00:06:22.917 position:30% line:89% align:start
a parting goal!

00:06:24.051 --> 00:06:27.555 position:30% line:83% align:start
It won't go in!
You won't fool me this time.

00:06:27.588 --> 00:06:28.556 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:06:30.625 --> 00:06:33.227 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>The ball dives down</i>
 <i>and bounces.</i>

00:06:33.261 --> 00:06:34.427 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:06:37.397 --> 00:06:38.165 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[cheering]
-[ann] <i>The...</i>

00:06:38.199 --> 00:06:39.834 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>The ball hits the net!</i>

00:06:39.867 --> 00:06:42.803 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu is now ahead</i>
 <i>in the match 4 to 3.</i>

00:06:42.837 --> 00:06:45.239 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>They're a step away</i>
 <i>from being champions.</i>

00:06:45.273 --> 00:06:46.374 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:06:46.406 --> 00:06:49.310 position:38% line:83% align:start
I did it.
I scored a goal, guys!

00:06:49.343 --> 00:06:51.913 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[cheering]
-You did it, Tsubasa.

00:06:51.946 --> 00:06:54.749 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>With this goal,</i>
 <i>Nankatsu is an inch away</i>

00:06:54.782 --> 00:06:56.617 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>from being crowned</i>
 <i>the champions.</i>

00:06:56.651 --> 00:06:58.586 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is the first time</i>
 <i>Nankatsu</i>

00:06:58.619 --> 00:07:00.221 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>carries the lead</i>
 <i>in the match.</i>

00:07:00.254 --> 00:07:01.289 position:41% line:89% align:start
[growl]

00:07:01.322 --> 00:07:03.456 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>It was</i>
 <i>a spectacular shot.</i>

00:07:03.490 --> 00:07:05.760 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>The ball flew diagonally,</i>
 <i>changing its direction</i>

00:07:05.793 --> 00:07:07.962 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>the moment it made contact</i>
 <i>with the turf,</i>

00:07:07.995 --> 00:07:09.797 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>to then going directly</i>
 <i>towards the goal.</i>

00:07:09.830 --> 00:07:11.165 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[cheering]
[ann] <i>This is</i>

00:07:11.198 --> 00:07:12.700 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>without a doubt a variant</i>
-We knew you could do it!

00:07:12.733 --> 00:07:14.035 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>of his normal Drive Shot.</i>
-Amazing!

00:07:14.068 --> 00:07:15.136 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>That's what I call</i>

00:07:15.169 --> 00:07:16.938 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>a Miracle Drive Shot,</i>
-Tsubasa scored a goal!

00:07:16.971 --> 00:07:17.638 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>ladies and gentlemen.</i>

00:07:17.672 --> 00:07:19.307 position:30% line:83% align:start
- <i>How exciting!</i>
-[grunt]

00:07:19.340 --> 00:07:20.641 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>Despite his injuries,</i>

00:07:20.675 --> 00:07:23.311 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa scores</i>
 <i>his fourth goal of the match</i>

00:07:23.344 --> 00:07:25.279 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>with a spectacular shot.</i>

00:07:25.313 --> 00:07:26.814 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>There's no doubt that</i>
 <i>this young man</i>

00:07:26.847 --> 00:07:29.183 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>is truly a gift</i>
 <i>for Japanese soccer.</i>

00:07:29.216 --> 00:07:31.218 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laugh]
-You did it, Tsubasa.

00:07:31.252 --> 00:07:33.154 position:16% line:83% align:start
We finally got a hold of
the lead.

00:07:33.187 --> 00:07:36.390 position:16% line:83% align:start
And we're a step away...
from finally achieving...

00:07:36.424 --> 00:07:38.826 position:24% line:83% align:start
our team's dream...
Ishizaki.

00:07:38.859 --> 00:07:40.294 position:41% line:83% align:start
[gasp]
Tsubasa?

00:07:40.328 --> 00:07:41.696 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
-Tsubasa!

00:07:41.729 --> 00:07:42.797 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:07:42.830 --> 00:07:43.698 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:07:43.731 --> 00:07:44.665 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Say something!
-Captain!

00:07:44.699 --> 00:07:46.567 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
-Wake up, man!

00:07:50.204 --> 00:07:51.339 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:07:51.372 --> 00:07:52.640 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:07:53.574 --> 00:07:55.376 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh, that's great news.
He's waking up.

00:07:55.409 --> 00:07:57.144 position:10% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa, how're you feeling?

00:07:58.279 --> 00:07:59.146 position:35% line:89% align:start
Where am I?

00:07:59.647 --> 00:08:01.215 position:27% line:89% align:start
In the infirmary.

00:08:01.248 --> 00:08:02.350 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:08:02.383 --> 00:08:03.517 position:21% line:89% align:start
What about the match?

00:08:03.551 --> 00:08:05.820 position:30% line:83% align:start
What happened?
I have to go back--

00:08:05.853 --> 00:08:06.554 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:08:06.587 --> 00:08:08.255 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
-You need more rest.

00:08:08.289 --> 00:08:10.358 position:24% line:83% align:start
Please, calm down,
young man.

00:08:10.391 --> 00:08:13.094 position:19% line:83% align:start
The match hasn't ended
just yet.

00:08:13.127 --> 00:08:14.028 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:08:14.061 --> 00:08:14.996 position:30% line:89% align:start
So I guess I...

00:08:15.663 --> 00:08:17.497 position:13% line:89% align:start
I fainted again, didn't I?

00:08:18.032 --> 00:08:18.966 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:21.102 position:24% line:83% align:start
But you did give us
the lead in the match

00:08:21.135 --> 00:08:22.770 position:21% line:89% align:start
with your last shot.

00:08:22.803 --> 00:08:23.537 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:08:23.571 --> 00:08:25.539 position:27% line:83% align:start
That was a really
amazing shot.

00:08:26.340 --> 00:08:27.541 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah...

00:08:27.975 --> 00:08:28.876 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:08:28.909 --> 00:08:30.244 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Where are you going?

00:08:30.277 --> 00:08:31.278 position:33% line:83% align:start
[cheerleader]
Let's go, Toho!

00:08:31.312 --> 00:08:32.380 position:21% line:89% align:start
Let's win this match!

00:08:32.413 --> 00:08:33.581 position:35% line:89% align:start
Sorimachi!

00:08:34.582 --> 00:08:35.850 position:41% line:83% align:start
[yell]
[grunt]

00:08:35.883 --> 00:08:37.018 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:08:37.051 --> 00:08:40.121 position:13% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And all of Nankatsu's</i>
 <i>defending desperately</i>

00:08:40.154 --> 00:08:42.256 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>in their captain's absence.</i>
-[panting]

00:08:42.289 --> 00:08:43.557 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Takeru]
Big Brother, why are you

00:08:43.591 --> 00:08:44.759 position:24% line:89% align:start
staring into space?

00:08:44.792 --> 00:08:46.127 position:16% line:89% align:start
What're you waiting for?

00:08:46.160 --> 00:08:47.561 position:16% line:89% align:start
You have to score a goal.

00:08:48.295 --> 00:08:49.363 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Ms. Hyuga]
 <i>Oh, Son...</i>

00:08:49.397 --> 00:08:50.464 position:35% line:89% align:start
Everyone...

00:08:50.498 --> 00:08:51.232 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
Hey, head coach...

00:08:51.265 --> 00:08:52.433 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:08:52.466 --> 00:08:54.301 position:19% line:83% align:start
Is this the first half
of the extra time

00:08:54.335 --> 00:08:55.403 position:30% line:89% align:start
or the second?

00:08:55.436 --> 00:08:57.004 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Furuoya]
The first one.

00:08:57.038 --> 00:08:59.407 position:24% line:83% align:start
Please, Head Coach,
let me play again.

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.342 position:16% line:83% align:start
Forgive me, but I can't,
Tsubasa.

00:09:01.375 --> 00:09:02.576 position:38% line:83% align:start
But why?
Why can't I play, sir?

00:09:02.610 --> 00:09:03.811 position:33% line:89% align:start
Just let me.

00:09:03.844 --> 00:09:07.281 position:16% line:83% align:start
Don't you worry, Tsubasa.
Nobody took your spot.

00:09:07.314 --> 00:09:08.449 position:27% line:89% align:start
Everyone else...

00:09:08.482 --> 00:09:10.818 position:21% line:83% align:start
is defending the goal
right now.

00:09:10.851 --> 00:09:12.953 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Ryo] Tsubasa collapsed
again, guys.

00:09:12.987 --> 00:09:13.754 position:24% line:89% align:start
And it's our fault

00:09:13.788 --> 00:09:15.322 position:30% line:83% align:start
for letting him
bear that burden.

00:09:15.356 --> 00:09:16.323 position:27% line:89% align:start
It doesn't matter

00:09:16.357 --> 00:09:18.692 position:24% line:83% align:start
if Tsubasa doesn't
come back again.

00:09:18.726 --> 00:09:20.394 position:24% line:83% align:start
We have to defend,
you hear me?

00:09:20.428 --> 00:09:22.329 position:10% line:89% align:start
He handed us this advantage.

00:09:22.363 --> 00:09:23.831 position:21% line:83% align:start
Don't worry about us,
Head Coach.

00:09:23.864 --> 00:09:26.200 position:21% line:83% align:start
Everyone, will defend
until he comes.

00:09:26.233 --> 00:09:27.234 position:24% line:89% align:start
Please, Head Coach.

00:09:27.268 --> 00:09:28.369 position:24% line:89% align:start
Don't sub him out!

00:09:28.402 --> 00:09:30.204 position:13% line:83% align:start
-Thanks to them, our coach
-Please, sir! We need him!

00:09:30.237 --> 00:09:32.206 position:19% line:89% align:start
didn't substitute you.

00:09:32.239 --> 00:09:33.407 position:35% line:89% align:start
Seriously?

00:09:33.441 --> 00:09:34.708 position:24% line:89% align:start
That exactly right,

00:09:34.742 --> 00:09:37.378 position:21% line:83% align:start
but I won't allow you
to be so careless.

00:09:37.411 --> 00:09:38.446 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:09:38.479 --> 00:09:40.014 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Furuoya]
In the second half, Yamamori

00:09:40.047 --> 00:09:42.016 position:21% line:83% align:start
-will take your spot.
-[grunting]

00:09:42.049 --> 00:09:44.085 position:13% line:83% align:start
Don't forget the agreement
we had.

00:09:44.118 --> 00:09:45.152 position:33% line:89% align:start
One more fall

00:09:45.186 --> 00:09:47.388 position:16% line:83% align:start
and we'll take you out of
the match, all right?

00:09:47.421 --> 00:09:48.489 position:13% line:89% align:start
But doctor it's just that--

00:09:48.523 --> 00:09:49.490 position:21% line:89% align:start
There's no more buts!

00:09:49.524 --> 00:09:51.192 position:16% line:83% align:start
Why are you so stubborn,
Tsubasa?

00:09:51.225 --> 00:09:52.193 position:33% line:89% align:start
Listen to me,

00:09:52.226 --> 00:09:54.762 position:19% line:83% align:start
the third championship
is just a silly whim.

00:09:54.795 --> 00:09:57.364 position:30% line:83% align:start
Your true dream
is to go to Brazil

00:09:57.398 --> 00:09:59.100 position:30% line:83% align:start
and be the best
in the world.

00:09:59.133 --> 00:09:59.934 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:10:00.935 --> 00:10:03.572 position:13% line:83% align:start
[reac] Yeah, and to achieve
that dream...

00:10:03.604 --> 00:10:05.773 position:21% line:83% align:start
First, I have to win
this match, or else...

00:10:05.806 --> 00:10:08.042 position:27% line:83% align:start
I won't feel like
I deserve it.

00:10:08.075 --> 00:10:09.043 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Hmm...
-Huh?

00:10:09.076 --> 00:10:11.011 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa] I have
a commitment to everyone

00:10:11.045 --> 00:10:11.745 position:33% line:89% align:start
in the team.

00:10:12.813 --> 00:10:15.349 position:19% line:83% align:start
I don't care if I risk
my professional career.

00:10:15.382 --> 00:10:16.684 position:19% line:89% align:start
Please, understand me.

00:10:16.717 --> 00:10:20.087 position:19% line:83% align:start
For me to go to Brazil,
I have to win here and now.

00:10:20.121 --> 00:10:22.524 position:13% line:83% align:start
I can't be the best player
in the world

00:10:22.557 --> 00:10:25.059 position:30% line:83% align:start
if I don't win
this match first.

00:10:25.092 --> 00:10:26.060 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm going to win,

00:10:26.093 --> 00:10:29.096 position:13% line:83% align:start
even if it's the last thing
I ever get to do.

00:10:31.298 --> 00:10:32.766 position:16% line:89% align:start
Please, let Tsubasa play.

00:10:32.800 --> 00:10:34.034 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:10:34.068 --> 00:10:36.337 position:27% line:83% align:start
It doesn't matter
if he wins or loses.

00:10:36.370 --> 00:10:38.105 position:33% line:83% align:start
For Tsubasa,
what's important

00:10:38.139 --> 00:10:41.242 position:21% line:83% align:start
is to play this match
until the end.

00:10:41.275 --> 00:10:42.109 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm begging you.

00:10:42.910 --> 00:10:45.112 position:30% line:83% align:start
Don't deny him
this opportunity.

00:10:47.281 --> 00:10:48.415 position:38% line:89% align:start
Sanae...

00:10:49.250 --> 00:10:50.017 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:10:50.050 --> 00:10:51.152 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:10:51.919 --> 00:10:54.188 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Don't dream of it.
-[grunt]

00:10:54.221 --> 00:10:56.056 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
[panting]

00:10:56.090 --> 00:10:57.391 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
Great sliding tackle,

00:10:57.424 --> 00:10:58.659 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Ishizaki.
-Huh?

00:10:58.692 --> 00:11:01.395 position:27% line:83% align:start
You defended like
true champions.

00:11:01.428 --> 00:11:03.565 position:21% line:89% align:start
Everybody, hear this.

00:11:03.598 --> 00:11:05.232 position:16% line:89% align:start
They're letting me play.

00:11:05.266 --> 00:11:06.300 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa.

00:11:06.333 --> 00:11:07.301 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laugh]
-Captain!

00:11:07.334 --> 00:11:08.369 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:11:08.402 --> 00:11:09.837 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>This is incredible.</i>

00:11:09.870 --> 00:11:11.071 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>Despite his injuries,</i>

00:11:11.105 --> 00:11:12.641 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>Nankatsu's number 10</i>
-We need you back!

00:11:12.673 --> 00:11:13.642 position:38% line:83% align:start
- <i>is back</i>
-That's it, Tsubasa!

00:11:13.674 --> 00:11:14.842 position:30% line:83% align:start
- <i>on the pitch.</i>
-You show 'em!

00:11:16.944 --> 00:11:19.648 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Now the ball's in</i>
 <i>Kojiro Hyuga's possession.</i>

00:11:19.680 --> 00:11:23.284 position:19% line:83% align:start
Stop him. Don't let him
shoot his Tiger Shot.

00:11:23.317 --> 00:11:24.285 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:11:25.520 --> 00:11:27.388 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:11:30.291 --> 00:11:31.825 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm coming, Hyuga.</i>

00:11:31.859 --> 00:11:33.160 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'll be here waiting.</i>

00:11:33.194 --> 00:11:36.330 position:13% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>We'll be right back</i>
 <i>with Captain Tsubasa.</i>

00:11:36.964 --> 00:11:38.465 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>And we're back.</i>

00:11:47.341 --> 00:11:48.409 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hyuga...

00:11:48.442 --> 00:11:51.712 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hyuga kicked it off bounds
so Tsubasa could come in.

00:11:51.745 --> 00:11:54.782 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Nankatsu's captain</i>
 <i>comes back to the pitch.</i>

00:11:54.815 --> 00:11:55.983 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Masao] <i>Tsubasa...</i>
-[Kazuo] <i>Tsubasa...</i>

00:11:56.016 --> 00:11:57.851 position:30% line:83% align:start
Great, Tsubasa.
I knew you'd come back.

00:11:57.885 --> 00:12:00.187 position:30% line:83% align:start
Now Nankatsu's
complete again.

00:12:00.221 --> 00:12:03.090 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa! Tsubasa!
-Tsubasa! Tsubasa!

00:12:03.123 --> 00:12:04.458 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
[ann] <i>And the stadium</i>

00:12:04.491 --> 00:12:05.960 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>receives Tsubasa</i>
-Tsubasa!

00:12:05.993 --> 00:12:07.995 position:30% line:83% align:start
- <i>with a chant.</i>
-Tsubasa!

00:12:08.028 --> 00:12:10.497 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa! Tsubasa!
-Tsubasa! Tsubasa!

00:12:10.532 --> 00:12:12.499 position:13% line:83% align:start
-We have to back up Hyuga!
-Tsubasa!

00:12:12.534 --> 00:12:15.469 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa! Tsubasa!
-Hyuga! Hyuga!

00:12:15.503 --> 00:12:17.972 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Hyuga! Hyuga!
-Tsubasa! Tsubasa!

00:12:18.005 --> 00:12:20.140 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Okay, here I am, Hyuga.</i>

00:12:20.174 --> 00:12:23.744 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro] <i>Let's finish</i>
 <i>this duel once and for all.</i>

00:12:23.777 --> 00:12:26.013 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa] <i>We'll give it</i>
 <i>our all until the end.</i>

00:12:26.046 --> 00:12:28.015 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro]
 <i>Until the very last moment.</i>

00:12:28.048 --> 00:12:29.049 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:12:29.083 --> 00:12:31.986 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa will</i>
 <i>take the throw-in.</i>

00:12:34.355 --> 00:12:36.457 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro] [grunt]
 <i>Tsubasa.</i>

00:12:36.490 --> 00:12:38.627 position:30% line:83% align:start
-What was that?
-Huh?

00:12:38.660 --> 00:12:41.028 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa passed</i>
 <i>Hyuga the ball!</i>

00:12:41.061 --> 00:12:43.897 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Is he actually thinking</i>
 <i>of facing him head on?</i>

00:12:43.931 --> 00:12:46.635 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa] <i>You'd better</i>
 <i>be ready, Hyuga.</i>

00:12:46.668 --> 00:12:47.034 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:12:48.135 --> 00:12:51.305 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro] <i>Are you seriously</i>
 <i>going to face me?</i>

00:12:51.338 --> 00:12:52.674 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>In your condition?</i>

00:12:52.707 --> 00:12:55.943 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
[yell]

00:12:55.976 --> 00:12:56.844 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
-Tsubasa!

00:12:56.877 --> 00:12:58.212 position:21% line:89% align:start
Pay attention, Toho.

00:12:58.245 --> 00:13:00.314 position:27% line:83% align:start
I want all of you
to attack right now.

00:13:00.347 --> 00:13:01.148 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:13:01.181 --> 00:13:02.550 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[panting]
-[ann] <i>Tsubasa couldn't</i>

00:13:02.584 --> 00:13:03.685 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>handle Hyuga,</i>

00:13:03.718 --> 00:13:04.885 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>and now all of Toho</i>

00:13:04.918 --> 00:13:06.655 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>is switching to offense.</i>
-[tiger growl]

00:13:06.688 --> 00:13:08.155 position:21% line:83% align:start
Get the ball from him
and now.

00:13:08.188 --> 00:13:09.256 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:13:09.290 --> 00:13:10.457 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Darn it all...</i>

00:13:10.491 --> 00:13:11.559 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Darn it all...</i>

00:13:11.593 --> 00:13:14.094 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>You think you won this,</i>
 <i>don't you?</i>

00:13:14.128 --> 00:13:15.029 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:13:15.062 --> 00:13:17.766 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is still...</i>
 <i>not over yet.</i>

00:13:17.798 --> 00:13:19.701 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:13:19.734 --> 00:13:21.636 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>This is</i>
 <i>an unprecedented match.</i>

00:13:21.670 --> 00:13:22.803 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:13:22.836 --> 00:13:24.905 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And the ball</i>
 <i>miraculously returns</i>

00:13:24.938 --> 00:13:26.273 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>to Tsubasa.</i>

00:13:26.307 --> 00:13:27.274 position:35% line:89% align:start
Take this!

00:13:27.308 --> 00:13:28.809 position:24% line:89% align:start
We've got you now!

00:13:28.842 --> 00:13:30.244 position:41% line:83% align:start
[gasp]
[grunt]

00:13:30.277 --> 00:13:33.180 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa's</i>
 <i>sent flying.</i>

00:13:33.213 --> 00:13:35.249 position:30% line:83% align:start
Pick on someone
your own size.

00:13:35.282 --> 00:13:36.150 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[scream]
-[grunt]

00:13:36.183 --> 00:13:38.085 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Ishizaki recovers</i>
 <i>the ball.</i>

00:13:38.118 --> 00:13:39.554 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>And by sheer coincidence,</i>

00:13:39.587 --> 00:13:41.355 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>the ball goes back</i>
 <i>to Tsubasa.</i>

00:13:41.388 --> 00:13:42.990 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu's captain</i>
 <i>is shaken up,</i>

00:13:43.023 --> 00:13:44.892 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>but makes an effort</i>
 <i>to maintain his balance</i>

00:13:44.925 --> 00:13:47.061 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>and control the ball.</i>
-[grunt]

00:13:47.094 --> 00:13:48.630 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>Here I go.</i>

00:13:48.663 --> 00:13:51.332 position:38% line:83% align:start
Nankatsu
for the third championship!

