Tsubasa maintains
his leadership

00:13:55.169 --> 00:13:56.771 position:21% line:83% align:start
despite his physical
condition.

00:13:56.805 --> 00:13:57.971 position:27% line:89% align:start
There's no doubt,

00:13:58.005 --> 00:14:01.543 position:24% line:83% align:start
that's exactly why
you're Nankatsu's captain.

00:14:01.576 --> 00:14:07.582 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:14:07.615 --> 00:14:08.817 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:14:08.849 --> 00:14:11.085 position:24% line:83% align:start
What're you doing?
Stop him right now!

00:14:11.118 --> 00:14:12.821 position:21% line:83% align:start
Don't just stay there
standing.

00:14:12.853 --> 00:14:14.789 position:33% line:83% align:start
Go after him!
What're you waiting for?

00:14:14.823 --> 00:14:16.190 position:19% line:89% align:start
