00:14:16.223 --> 00:14:17.491 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Yeah! Yeah!
-Yeah! Yeah!

00:14:17.525 --> 00:14:20.327 position:24% line:83% align:start
We'll show you how
Toho Academy really defends.

00:14:20.361 --> 00:14:21.696 position:21% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa, be careful!

00:14:21.730 --> 00:14:22.863 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
[grunt]

00:14:22.896 --> 00:14:24.799 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa makes</i>
 <i>a miraculous pass</i>

00:14:24.833 --> 00:14:27.535 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>just before they can</i>
 <i>steal the ball from him.</i>

00:14:27.569 --> 00:14:28.469 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:14:29.336 --> 00:14:31.105 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa reeled in</i>
 <i>the defense</i>

00:14:31.138 --> 00:14:33.874 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>so we could advance freely.</i>

00:14:33.907 --> 00:14:34.975 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:14:35.008 --> 00:14:36.511 position:33% line:83% align:start
We can't let
this opportunity

00:14:36.544 --> 00:14:38.513 position:19% line:83% align:start
-go to waste, everyone.
-No!

00:14:38.546 --> 00:14:40.615 position:13% line:89% align:start
We'll protect Wakashimazu.

00:14:40.648 --> 00:14:42.483 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'd love to see that!

