[grunt]

00:14:43.484 --> 00:14:44.619 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:14:44.652 --> 00:14:46.153 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Nankatsu</i>
 <i>makes headway</i>

00:14:46.186 --> 00:14:47.555 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>with a series of passes.</i>

00:14:47.589 --> 00:14:49.791 position:16% line:83% align:start
Now's our time to shine,
Takasugi.

00:14:49.824 --> 00:14:51.191 position:24% line:83% align:start
-We have to attack.
-Yeah!

00:14:51.225 --> 00:14:52.259 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>I won't let you through.</i>
-[gasp]

00:14:52.292 --> 00:14:53.661 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[ann] <i>Sawada rejects</i>

00:14:53.695 --> 00:14:54.194 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>the ball.</i>

00:14:55.095 --> 00:14:56.698 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>But Ishizaki receives it,</i>
-[grunt]

00:14:56.731 --> 00:14:58.132 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>anticipating the move.</i>

00:14:58.165 --> 00:14:59.634 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Ryo]
 <i>Good, it's my turn.</i>

00:14:59.667 --> 00:15:00.668 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[Tsubasa] Ishizaki,
-[growl]

00:15:00.702 --> 00:15:01.836 position:33% line:83% align:start
-be careful!
-Huh?

00:15:01.870 --> 00:15:02.970 position:35% line:89% align:start
Behind you!

00:15:03.003 --> 00:15:04.539 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[yell]
-[tiger growl]

00:15:04.572 --> 00:15:05.939 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
[yell]

00:15:05.973 --> 00:15:08.909 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Ishizaki feels</i>
 <i>the threat and passes it.</i>

00:15:08.942 --> 00:15:10.411 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[scream]
-[grunt]

00:15:11.345 --> 00:15:13.715 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll kick it towards</i>
 <i>the right side.</i>

