[yell]

00:15:15.583 --> 00:15:18.452 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Izawa takes a shot</i>
 <i>outside the danger zone</i>

00:15:18.485 --> 00:15:20.889 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the ball spins</i>
 <i>towards the right side.</i>

