[yell]

00:15:21.689 --> 00:15:22.423 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:15:23.357 --> 00:15:25.125 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>If I don't win</i>
 <i>the tournament, Dad,</i>

00:15:25.159 --> 00:15:25.660 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'll quit soccer.</i>

00:15:26.994 --> 00:15:30.665 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll stop this shot,</i>
 <i>for my honor and my pride!</i>

00:15:30.698 --> 00:15:32.132 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>The goalkeeper</i>
 <i>has it,</i>

00:15:32.166 --> 00:15:33.835 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>despite</i>
 <i>the difficult angle.</i>

00:15:33.868 --> 00:15:35.269 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>The keeper Wakashimazu's</i>
-[grunt]

00:15:35.302 --> 00:15:37.438 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>able to stop it</i>
 <i>with one hand.</i>

00:15:37.471 --> 00:15:38.939 position:21% line:89% align:start
No, it's impossible.

00:15:38.972 --> 00:15:41.942 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>With this,</i>
 <i>Wakashimazu reminds Nankatsu</i>

00:15:41.975 --> 00:15:44.646 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>that they're still</i>
 <i>in the game.</i>

00:15:44.679 --> 00:15:45.245 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:46.213 --> 00:15:49.049 position:19% line:83% align:start
I thought that his arm
was still injured.

00:15:49.082 --> 00:15:51.452 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll fulfill my promise,</i>
 <i>Dad.</i>

00:15:51.485 --> 00:15:52.386 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:15:52.419 --> 00:15:54.021 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>And the referee whistles</i>

00:15:54.054 --> 00:15:55.389 position:13% line:83% align:start
- <i>the end of the first half</i>
-[groaning]

00:15:55.422 --> 00:15:56.558 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>of extra time.</i>

00:15:56.591 --> 00:15:57.926 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:15:57.958 --> 00:15:59.059 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
[gasps]

00:15:59.092 --> 00:16:00.227 position:19% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa, are you okay?

00:16:00.260 --> 00:16:03.263 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Come on, Captain!
-Tsubasa, are you okay?

00:16:03.297 --> 00:16:06.901 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:16:06.935 --> 00:16:09.403 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Uhh...
-Uhh...

00:16:09.436 --> 00:16:11.438 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:16:12.372 --> 00:16:13.508 position:35% line:89% align:start
Everyone...

00:16:13.541 --> 00:16:15.810 position:13% line:89% align:start
What do you need, Tsubasa?

00:16:15.844 --> 00:16:18.847 position:13% line:89% align:start
I, want to, play with you.

00:16:18.880 --> 00:16:21.114 position:21% line:89% align:start
Until the...very end.

00:16:21.148 --> 00:16:22.349 position:41% line:83% align:start
-What?
-What?

00:16:23.450 --> 00:16:24.084 position:21% line:89% align:start
But they will not...

00:16:24.953 --> 00:16:27.689 position:27% line:83% align:start
allow me to play
like I always have.

00:16:27.722 --> 00:16:28.422 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:16:29.256 --> 00:16:31.425 position:30% line:83% align:start
If I'm a burden
to everybody...

00:16:32.259 --> 00:16:33.895 position:13% line:89% align:start
you need to switch me out.

00:16:33.928 --> 00:16:35.663 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-Tsubasa...

00:16:36.531 --> 00:16:37.799 position:19% line:89% align:start
If you would rather...

00:16:37.832 --> 00:16:40.300 position:35% line:83% align:start
me not play
with you guys anymore.

00:16:40.334 --> 00:16:42.302 position:30% line:83% align:start
I will respect
your decision.

00:16:43.505 --> 00:16:45.339 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Uhh...
-Uhh...

00:16:45.372 --> 00:16:47.374 position:13% line:83% align:start
-We want you to stay here.
-[laugh]

00:16:47.407 --> 00:16:48.175 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:16:48.208 --> 00:16:49.209 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laughs]
-This amazing adventure

00:16:49.243 --> 00:16:51.178 position:13% line:89% align:start
started with us as a team.

00:16:51.211 --> 00:16:53.347 position:16% line:83% align:start
So right now, we have to
finish this journey

00:16:53.380 --> 00:16:54.414 position:35% line:89% align:start
as a team.

00:16:55.650 --> 00:16:56.416 position:27% line:89% align:start
Are you serious?

00:16:57.484 --> 00:17:00.889 position:19% line:83% align:start
So that means, you guys
want me to keep playing?

00:17:00.922 --> 00:17:03.056 position:19% line:89% align:start
Do you wanna know why?

00:17:03.090 --> 00:17:04.091 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Because you are
-Because you are

00:17:04.124 --> 00:17:06.093 position:33% line:83% align:start
-our captain!
-our captain!

00:17:06.126 --> 00:17:07.461 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
My brothers...

00:17:09.162 --> 00:17:10.397 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Takeru]
Hey, Mom...

00:17:10.430 --> 00:17:12.199 position:33% line:83% align:start
How come when
Tsubasa wasn't on the pitch,

00:17:12.232 --> 00:17:14.569 position:10% line:83% align:start
my bro didn't want to shoot,
not even once?

00:17:14.602 --> 00:17:15.402 position:35% line:89% align:start
Why's that?

00:17:15.435 --> 00:17:17.271 position:33% line:83% align:start
You know how
your older brother is.

00:17:17.304 --> 00:17:18.540 position:30% line:83% align:start
The only thing
he wants in life

00:17:18.573 --> 00:17:21.275 position:19% line:83% align:start
is to face off against
Tsubasa until the end.

00:17:21.308 --> 00:17:23.811 position:19% line:83% align:start
I think, it's dangerous
for him to play like that.

00:17:23.845 --> 00:17:25.045 position:16% line:83% align:start
-But everyone here knows
-Huh?

00:17:25.078 --> 00:17:26.781 position:33% line:83% align:start
that Tsubasa
is never giving up.

00:17:26.814 --> 00:17:27.882 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right.

00:17:27.916 --> 00:17:29.717 position:27% line:83% align:start
He plans to play
until the last minute

00:17:29.751 --> 00:17:31.084 position:27% line:89% align:start
without a worry.

00:17:31.118 --> 00:17:32.720 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Koji]
Just a one goal advantage.

00:17:32.754 --> 00:17:35.489 position:21% line:83% align:start
If they defend well,
we'll win the tournament.

00:17:35.523 --> 00:17:36.456 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:17:36.490 --> 00:17:38.560 position:30% line:83% align:start
Hyuga can turn
the scoreboard around, guys.

00:17:38.593 --> 00:17:39.661 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't you all worry.

00:17:39.694 --> 00:17:42.229 position:10% line:83% align:start
I thought Toho Academy could
win on all three levels:

00:17:42.262 --> 00:17:44.164 position:13% line:83% align:start
middle school, high school
and university.

00:17:44.197 --> 00:17:45.567 position:13% line:89% align:start
But that might not happen.

00:17:45.600 --> 00:17:46.568 position:30% line:89% align:start
Toho Academy...

00:17:46.601 --> 00:17:49.236 position:16% line:83% align:start
has demonstrated to have
great fighting spirit.

00:17:49.269 --> 00:17:50.972 position:10% line:89% align:start
Surpassing their reputation.

00:17:51.005 --> 00:17:51.906 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:17:51.940 --> 00:17:53.106 position:38% line:83% align:start
You know
the tournament's results

00:17:53.140 --> 00:17:54.576 position:13% line:89% align:start
don't matter to me anymore.

00:17:54.609 --> 00:17:57.177 position:21% line:83% align:start
And I'm very proud of
all of our students.

00:17:57.210 --> 00:17:58.211 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>Team Nankatsu...</i>

00:17:58.245 --> 00:17:59.346 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Furuoya]
It's time now.

00:17:59.379 --> 00:18:02.249 position:30% line:83% align:start
I want you guys
to give it all out there.

00:18:02.282 --> 00:18:03.450 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:18:03.483 --> 00:18:04.484 position:30% line:89% align:start
It was an honor

00:18:04.519 --> 00:18:06.219 position:16% line:83% align:start
to have been your coach,
guys.

00:18:06.253 --> 00:18:09.524 position:24% line:83% align:start
Play with your all,
and don't you get cocky.

00:18:09.557 --> 00:18:10.525 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:18:11.793 --> 00:18:12.694 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Kitazume]
Hyuga.

00:18:12.727 --> 00:18:12.961 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:12.994 --> 00:18:14.161 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:14.194 --> 00:18:16.731 position:21% line:83% align:start
I want you to play to
your hearts' content.

00:18:16.764 --> 00:18:18.967 position:10% line:89% align:start
Everyone is counting on you.

00:18:19.000 --> 00:18:20.467 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah...

00:18:20.500 --> 00:18:21.468 position:35% line:89% align:start
Captain...

00:18:22.102 --> 00:18:23.037 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah...

