Yes, sir!

00:18:24.204 --> 00:18:26.239 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[cheering]
-[ann] <i>The last ten minutes</i>

00:18:26.273 --> 00:18:28.175 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>of the match</i>
 <i>are about to begin.</i>

00:18:28.208 --> 00:18:29.209 position:27% line:89% align:start
Let's go, Hyuga!

00:18:29.242 --> 00:18:29.844 position:30% line:89% align:start
Let's win this!

00:18:31.211 --> 00:18:33.347 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And it's Toho's</i>
 <i>turn to get the kick-off.</i>

00:18:33.380 --> 00:18:34.281 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:18:34.749 --> 00:18:36.084 position:27% line:89% align:start
Is he defending?

00:18:36.116 --> 00:18:37.250 position:27% line:89% align:start
But why is that?

00:18:37.284 --> 00:18:38.720 position:38% line:83% align:start
Hold on,
if I'm correct,

00:18:38.753 --> 00:18:41.121 position:21% line:83% align:start
the last time Tsubasa
played as a defender

00:18:41.154 --> 00:18:43.024 position:27% line:83% align:start
was in the match
against Shutetsu.

00:18:43.057 --> 00:18:43.290 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Hyuga...</i>

00:18:44.424 --> 00:18:47.194 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll wait for you to shoot</i>
 <i>to counterattack.</i>

00:18:47.227 --> 00:18:48.328 position:24% line:89% align:start
I don't understand.

00:18:48.362 --> 00:18:49.998 position:24% line:89% align:start
What's he scheming?

00:18:50.031 --> 00:18:51.599 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Sounds good to me, Tsubasa.</i>

00:18:51.633 --> 00:18:53.067 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>If that's how</i>
 <i>you want to play,</i>

00:18:53.101 --> 00:18:53.935 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>that's fine by me.</i>

00:18:53.968 --> 00:18:54.569 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:18:55.503 --> 00:18:57.304 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Hyuga the Tiger</i>
 <i>immediately</i>

00:18:57.337 --> 00:18:58.438 position:21% line:83% align:start
- <i>winds up to shoot.</i>
-[grunt]

