00:19:12.152 --> 00:19:13.788 position:24% line:89% align:start
Here comes the tie.

00:19:13.821 --> 00:19:15.523 position:35% line:89% align:start
Take this!

00:19:15.556 --> 00:19:17.457 position:30% line:89% align:start
My Tiger Shot!

00:19:17.491 --> 00:19:18.893 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:19:18.926 --> 00:19:20.427 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>I will not lose.</i>

00:19:20.460 --> 00:19:21.729 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:19:21.763 --> 00:19:22.964 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>You have to stop it.</i>

00:19:22.997 --> 00:19:24.532 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Stop it, Tsubasa.</i>

00:19:26.233 --> 00:19:29.469 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Because you are</i>
 <i>Nankatsu's captain.</i>

00:19:30.805 --> 00:19:34.142 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And Tsubasa</i>
 <i>stops the Tiger Shot!</i>

00:19:34.174 --> 00:19:35.442 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:19:35.843 --> 00:19:36.911 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:19:36.944 --> 00:19:37.845 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:19:37.879 --> 00:19:39.379 position:33% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa, no!

00:19:42.517 --> 00:19:45.119 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro]
 <i>Tsubasa, in all honesty...</i>

00:19:45.153 --> 00:19:46.521 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>you're admirable.</i>

00:19:47.689 --> 00:19:49.624 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>But I won't give up!</i>

00:19:49.657 --> 00:19:50.925 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Are you okay, Tsubasa?
