00:19:50.958 --> 00:19:52.192 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>you're injured.</i>

00:19:53.061 --> 00:19:54.729 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'm finally
going to finish you

00:19:54.762 --> 00:19:57.031 position:16% line:89% align:start
once and for all, Tsubasa

00:19:57.065 --> 00:19:59.033 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yells]

00:19:59.067 --> 00:20:00.668 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:00.702 --> 00:20:02.737 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:20:02.770 --> 00:20:03.403 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:20:03.437 --> 00:20:05.272 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>We'll protect you.</i>

00:20:05.305 --> 00:20:07.008 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>They won't get through us.</i>

00:20:07.041 --> 00:20:08.776 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>We'll help you, Tsubasa.</i>

00:20:08.810 --> 00:20:09.744 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:20:10.178 --> 00:20:11.445 position:35% line:89% align:start
You idiots!

00:20:12.212 --> 00:20:13.447 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Now everyone attack!
-[yells]

00:20:13.480 --> 00:20:14.615 position:19% line:89% align:start
We have to give Tsubasa

00:20:14.649 --> 00:20:16.684 position:35% line:83% align:start
enough time
to recover, guys!

00:20:16.718 --> 00:20:18.218 position:13% line:83% align:start
-We won't let you through!
-[yells]

00:20:18.251 --> 00:20:20.922 position:27% line:83% align:start
We won't let you
score another goal!

00:20:20.955 --> 00:20:23.290 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Both teams are</i>
 <i>fighting over the ball.</i>

00:20:23.323 --> 00:20:25.526 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>No one is</i>
 <i>willing to budge.</i>

00:20:25.560 --> 00:20:26.460 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's mine!

00:20:27.227 --> 00:20:28.495 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>This is incredible.</i>

00:20:28.529 --> 00:20:31.599 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>The keeper Wakashimazu</i>
 <i>has the ball.</i>

00:20:31.632 --> 00:20:32.633 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain!

00:20:34.001 --> 00:20:34.802 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:34.836 --> 00:20:36.504 position:16% line:89% align:start
You have to score a goal!

00:20:36.537 --> 00:20:40.240 position:19% line:83% align:start
Only you can bring Toho
to victory, Captain.

00:20:40.273 --> 00:20:41.843 position:30% line:89% align:start
Wakashimazu...

00:20:41.876 --> 00:20:44.178 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:20:44.212 --> 00:20:45.312 position:27% line:89% align:start
Everyone, attack!

00:20:45.345 --> 00:20:46.514 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:20:46.547 --> 00:20:50.118 position:19% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa, say something.
You have to wake up.

00:20:50.151 --> 00:20:52.252 position:16% line:83% align:start
The ball is your friend,
remember?

00:20:52.285 --> 00:20:53.688 position:10% line:89% align:start
You yourself taught me that.

00:20:53.721 --> 00:20:54.822 position:27% line:89% align:start
Please, wake up.

00:20:55.322 --> 00:20:56.323 position:27% line:89% align:start
Wake up, Captain.

00:20:57.024 --> 00:20:58.325 position:10% line:89% align:start
We'll be defending the goal.

00:20:58.358 --> 00:20:59.694 position:30% line:89% align:start
The two of us.

00:21:00.260 --> 00:21:01.162 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:21:01.195 --> 00:21:02.429 position:35% line:89% align:start
Morisaki...

00:21:02.462 --> 00:21:06.134 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>The captain trusts in</i>
 <i>my play to support him.</i>

00:21:06.167 --> 00:21:07.367 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's yours, Captain.

00:21:07.400 --> 00:21:09.704 position:24% line:83% align:start
-He's gonna shoot!
-We have to prevent that!

00:21:09.737 --> 00:21:10.505 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't let him shoot.

00:21:10.538 --> 00:21:12.673 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>If you overuse</i>
 <i>your Tiger Shot,</i>

00:21:12.707 --> 00:21:15.743 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>it'll be counterproductive</i>
 <i>in the end, Hyuga.</i>

00:21:15.777 --> 00:21:17.277 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Mr. Kira]
 <i>Don't lose your cool.</i>

00:21:17.310 --> 00:21:17.979 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Be careful, Kojiro.</i>

00:21:19.180 --> 00:21:21.448 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro] <i>If we win</i>
 <i>the championship...</i>

00:21:21.481 --> 00:21:24.919 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll show everyone</i>
 <i>I'm better than Tsubasa.</i>

00:21:24.952 --> 00:21:26.154 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-What?

00:21:26.187 --> 00:21:27.420 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hyuga!

00:21:27.454 --> 00:21:28.790 position:24% line:89% align:start
Well done, Kojiro!

00:21:29.857 --> 00:21:32.392 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Sorimachi receives</i>
 <i>the ball wide open.</i>

00:21:32.425 --> 00:21:34.829 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is the opportunity</i>
 <i>Toho needs.</i>

00:21:34.862 --> 00:21:36.264 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
[yell]

00:21:36.296 --> 00:21:37.598 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:21:38.599 --> 00:21:41.235 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And there's</i>
 <i>the keeper, everyone.</i>

00:21:41.269 --> 00:21:42.469 position:19% line:89% align:start
I stopped it, Tsubasa.

00:21:43.370 --> 00:21:44.437 position:16% line:83% align:start
-[ann] <i>But the ball is in</i>
-[gasp]

00:21:44.471 --> 00:21:46.406 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>possession of</i>
 <i>the forward Sawada.</i>

00:21:46.439 --> 00:21:47.340 position:16% line:89% align:start
This can't be happening.

00:21:47.374 --> 00:21:48.743 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's mine!

00:21:49.811 --> 00:21:52.580 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa stops</i>
 <i>the ball with his face.</i>

00:21:52.613 --> 00:21:54.916 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>What a way to put</i>
 <i>his body on the line,</i>

00:21:54.949 --> 00:21:56.150 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>literally.</i>

00:21:56.184 --> 00:21:57.819 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>The ball is my friend.</i>

00:21:57.852 --> 00:21:59.086 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I don't have to fear it.</i>

00:22:00.621 --> 00:22:02.256 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro]
 <i>No, but why?</i>

00:22:02.290 --> 00:22:05.026 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Why can't I just beat him</i>
 <i>already?</i>

00:22:06.227 --> 00:22:07.595 position:21% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa, be careful.

00:22:08.196 --> 00:22:09.263 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's enough.

00:22:09.297 --> 00:22:11.199 position:30% line:83% align:start
I can't bear to
keep watching.

00:22:11.232 --> 00:22:12.533 position:35% line:89% align:start
Calm down.

00:22:12.567 --> 00:22:18.005 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hyuga, I'm begging you,
don't hurt Tsubasa anymore.

00:22:18.039 --> 00:22:19.740 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>He can't stand on two feet,</i>

00:22:19.774 --> 00:22:22.844 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>yet he's still hanging in,</i>
 <i>fighting.</i>

00:22:22.877 --> 00:22:26.214 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Where's he drawing</i>
 <i>the will to play from?</i>

00:22:26.247 --> 00:22:27.215 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Is it a dream?</i>

00:22:27.248 --> 00:22:28.115 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>A promise?</i>

00:22:28.950 --> 00:22:30.918 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I don't understand why.</i>

00:22:30.952 --> 00:22:33.453 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Why can't I beat Tsubasa?</i>

